--- /dev/null
+++ b/extra/sparsehash/sparsehash-2.0.4/doc/sparse_hash_map.html
@@ -0,0 +1,1719 @@
+<HTML>
+<!-- The API of this class and the documentation -- but not the
+     implementation! -- are based on that for SGI's hash_map class,
+     augmented with tr1 support.
+  -->
+<!--
