+</TD>
+<TD VAlign=top>
+   The hash_set's key and value type.  This is also defined as
+   <tt>sparse_hash_set::key_type</tt> and
+   <tt>sparse_hash_set::value_type</tt>.
+</TD>
+<TD VAlign=top>
+   &nbsp;
+</TD>
+</TR>
+
+<TR>
+<TD VAlign=top>
